title: TaTi$_{7}$ (BCC SQS-16) Structure
comments:
This is a special quasirandom structure with 16 atoms per unit cell (SQS-16) for a bcc binary substitutional alloy A$_{x}$B$_{1-x}$ (Jiang, 2004; Chakraborty, 2016)). 
 Several compositions are available: \begin{itemize} \item \href{current_web_home_dir/AB7_hR16_166_c_c2h-001}{TaTi$_{7}$ (AB7\_hR16\_166\_c\_c2h)} (this structure), \item \href{current_web_home_dir/A3B13_oC32_38_ac_a2bcdef-001}{Ta$_{3}$Ti$_{13}$ (A3B13\_oC32\_38\_ac\_a2bcdef)}, \item \href{current_web_home_dir/AB3_mC32_8_4a_12a-001}{TaTi$_{3}$-I (AB3\_mC32\_8\_4a\_12a)} , \item \href{current_web_home_dir/AB3_mC32_8_4a_4a4b-001}{TaTi$_{3}$-II (AB3\_mC32\_8\_4a\_4a4b)} , \item \href{current_web_home_dir/A5B11_mP16_6_2abc_2a3b3c-001}{Ta$_{5}$Ti$_{11}$ (A5B11\_mP16\_6\_2abc\_2a3b3c)} , \item \href{current_web_home_dir/A3B5_oC32_38_abcd_abcef-001}{Ta$_{3}$Ti$_{8}$ (A3B5\_oC32\_38\_abce\_abcdf)} , \item \href{current_web_home_dir/AB_aP16_2_4i_4i-001}{TaTi (AB\_aP16\_2\_4i\_4i)}. \end{itemize}
